    "For example, the order of 3 for a pair of atoms means that there are two other vertices on the shortest path between this pair of atoms.",
    "In R-MAT we used 4 as the maximum order of neighborhood distance.",
    "That is, we encoded as separate features if two atoms are 1, 2, 3 or 4 hops away in the molecular graph.",
    "In Table 5 (b) we ablate this choice.",
    "The result suggests that R-MAT performance benefits from including separate features for all the considered orders."
